title: U.S. imports of trade goods from China 1985 to 2019
yAxis: Import volume in billion U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Import volume in billion U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 35.
In general Import volume in billion U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2018 and 2019.
The highest Import volume in billion U.S. dollars, of value 539.67 was reached at Year 2018
Minimum Import volume in billion U.S. dollars about 3.86 was reached at Year 1985
